com.joliciel.talismane.parser

Class DependencyArc

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.joliciel.talismane.parser.DependencyArc
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<DependencyArc>

    public class DependencyArc
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<DependencyArc>
    A dependency arc, indicating a dependency relationship between two pos-tagged tokens, one of which is the head and one of which is the dependent, with a particular functional label (e.g. subject, direct object, etc.).
    Author:
    Assaf Urieli
